Class LinkedListDS

  • java.lang.Object
    • LinkedListDS

  • public class LinkedListDS
extends java.lang.Object
    Doubly Linked List Data Structure takes randomly generated number and creates doubly linked list using bubble sort it sorts the linked list, then deletes an element which is chosen based on the sorting order, then inserts a new element of value 10
